    "body": "Hi @BenTScott \r\n\r\nIf you have the same index name more than once, you need to specify `indexId`:\r\n\r\n```js\r\n.index({ indexName: 'instant_search', indexId: 'second' })\r\n```\r\n\r\nLet me know how it goes.",
